1、田中平編著，1994，最新半等體製造學，復漢出版社，臺南2、賴耿陽編著，1987，薄膜製作工藝學，復漢出版社，臺南3、Peter 
            Van Zant, 2000, Microchip Fabrication, McGraw-Hill Companies, Inc., 
            New York4、J.H. Moore, C. C. Davis, M.A. Coplan, Building 
            Scientific Apparatus, 1988 Addison Wesley Publ. Co. Inc., 
            Workingham, United Kingdom


